User Registration app
1. Building an app using Spring MVC and Spring ORM


How to create a Spring MVC and Spring ORM project (3 steps):
1. Create the Maven project and update the pom with the needed dependencies 
2. Configure the Front Controller (DispatcherServlet) by creating a web.xml
3. Configure spring config file which we will configure ORM configurations.
   ORM configuratoins consists of configuring the HibernateTemplate. 
   To configure the HibernateTemplate, we must configure:
	a. the SessionFactory
	b. DataSource
	c. ViewResolver 
4. Configure the MVC design pattern, which consists of:
	a. Model 
	b. Data Access Layer
	c. Service Layer
	d. Controller Layer
